🌟 Emoji Search Application 🚀
Welcome to Emoji Search, the fun and fast way to find the perfect emoji for any occasion! 🌈 Whether you're texting friends, crafting social media posts, or just want to add a little flair to your day, Emoji Search has got you covered.



Overview
Emojee is a fun and interactive web application designed to help users search for and copy emojis easily. With a simple interface and categorized buttons, Emojee allows users to find the perfect emoji for any occasion, enhancing their messaging experience.
🎉 Features
Use emojis to highlight key features or call out important information. For example:
Search Functionality 🔍
Categorized Buttons 📂
Clipboard Copy 📋


